Catherine Samie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catherine_Samie 0 Catherine Samie (born 3 February 1933) is a French actress and member (sociétaire, doyen) of the Comédie-Française from 1962. On July 14, 2011, she became Grand Officier of the Legion of Honor. She is a Catholic.
